org.jnosql.artemis.graph

Interface VertexTraversal

  • All Superinterfaces:
    VertexConditionTraversal

    public interface VertexTraversal
extends VertexConditionTraversal
    The Graph Traversal that maps Vertex. This Traversal is lazy, in other words, that just run after any finalizing method.
